Install Instructions
======================================================================
Requirements: node

Node modules: formidable, sequelize

1. create models/db_info.js and paste into it:

   exports.db = '';
   exports.user = '';
   exports.pw = '';

   Fill in your db, user and password.
   
2. Run node build_db.js in the models directory.

3. (Optional) Run node test_data.js in the models directory, so you
   can test your installation.

4. To start the server, you have two options:
     a) modify the paths in start.sh [production|development]
     b) run the following:
       If running on production server:
         $ export NODE_ENV=production
         $ node index.js

       On localhost/development:
         $ NODE_ENV=development node index.js
